quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  7,40,"That those who lied/denied/falsified with Our verses/evidences and became arrogant from/about it, the sky`s/space`s doors/entrances do not be (get) opened for them, and nor they enter the Paradise, until the camel enters/penetrates in the needle`s/sewing needle`s eye/threading hole, and as/like that We reward/reimburse the criminals/sinners"
  7,41,"For them from Hell (is a) bed/crib , and from above them covers/darknesses , and as/like that We reward/reimburse the unjust/oppressors"
  7,42,"And those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds, We do not burden/impose a self except its endurance/capacity , those are the Paradises` owners/company , they are in it immortally/eternally"
  7,43,"And We removed/took away what (is) in their chests (innermosts) from hatred/spite/animosity , the rivers flow from beneath them , and they said: \"The praise/gratitude/thanks (is) to God who guided us to this, and we were not to (be) guided had it not been for that God guided us. Our Lord`s messengers had come with the truth .\" And they (those who believed) were called: \"That (is) the Paradise you were made to inherit it becuase (of) what you were making/doing/working"
  7,44,"And the Paradises` owners/company called/cried (to) the fire`s owners/company: \"That we had found what our Lord promised us truthful/factually , so did you find what your Lord promised truthfully/factually ?\" They said: \"Yes.\" So an announcer/informer (from) between them announced/informed : \"That God`s curse/torture (is) on the unjust/oppressors"
  7,45,"Those who prevent/obstruct from God`s way/path and they desire it (be) bent/crookedness , and they are with the end (other life) disbelieving"
  7,46,"And between them (B) (is) a partition/barrier/protection , and on the fence between Heaven and Hell/the highest tip of anything (are) men they know each/all with (by) their marks/identifications/expressions, and they called/cried (to) the Paradises` company/friends : \"That a greeting/security/peace on you.\" They did not enter it and they are coveting/desiring"
  7,47,"And if their eye sights/understanding was diverted towards the fire`s company/friends , they said: \"Our Lord do not make/put us with the nation the unjust/oppressive"